data.description: Are you looking for a home with an abundance of square footage, a good layout, and tons of possibility? Then this 3 bed, 2 bath, 2 car home is for you! Purchase this property for as little as 3% down! This property is approved for HomePath Mortgage Financing. This property is approved for HomePath Renovation Mortgage Financing.
